original_title: Power Rangers Time Force: Photo Finish
overview: An new film is being shot downtown, and the Rangers are interested in checking it out, but eventually the filming turned-out to be a scam that a Mutant was filming the movie in which is called "The End of the Power Rangers" which eventually all six Rangers were put in different films, Lucas is in a Samurai movie, Katie is in a Musical, Jen is in a Kung-fu movie, Wes and Trip are in a Western, and Eric is in a Jungle movie. All the Rangers tries their best to get out of the whole Movie Madness.
title: Power Rangers Time Force: Photo Finish
